{"tid":58414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(恐怖)消失的一雙腿 六位女孩合照卻只有10隻腳!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-12-28T19:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T23:59:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f965cae9d644d12e584dade336ef8cc51cc9ab84","tid":58414,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ToIeZkx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FToIeZkx.jpg&h=07fc3f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界上許多事情無法用科學的角度解釋它的原因，國外有網友在《Reddit》網站中分享了一張照片，照片中六位女孩坐在沙發上開心合影，但仔細一看卻有著驚人的發現，照片中有六個人卻只有五雙腿。<br />\n照片越看越不對勁，六位女孩照理來說應該要有六雙腿，而消失的一雙腿究竟去哪了呢？不管怎麼數，照片中就是只有10隻腳，令人毛骨悚然。<br />\n但也有人認為，應該是視角的關係，導致其中一位女孩的腿被擋住，所以才會少一雙腿，<span style=\"color: red;\">這張詭譎的照片，至今還是沒有解答。</span>"},{"pid":"b6ca658562caf8c587360c92c00cbe57b975c344","tid":58414,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:15:22.000Z","msg":"中間兩個收埋左一隻腳"},{"pid":"27908ecae215f6b13ae7f28e05d4e20b4b066f69","tid":58414,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中間兩個收埋左一隻腳</blockquote><br />\n錯"},{"pid":"ae5166630a775e761aa23fc3ce65936eace4e6c5","tid":58414,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:26:50.000Z","msg":"仆街，少左一對無得奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59b60c01dca6305abb8cdd3427e143a4f96e391","tid":58414,"uid":10242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:28:44.000Z","msg":"三條黑腳"},{"pid":"74528dd64562a1955d0304ab664104c947fdfedf","tid":58414,"uid":57489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:29:46.000Z","msg":"左三係key上去囉咁簡單"},{"pid":"28c4ea83658ca465cf8ee6a62874ddf1e7fd1d2b","tid":58414,"uid":34308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T19:33:35.000Z","msg":"左2 2條褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomo